      <h3 style="color:#fc8f39;">MILESTONES</h3>
      <p>A journey of thousand miles begins with a single step. This was the very first step in 1975 when a new firm was established as "Shree Chintamani Builders". The first residential project was completed in the same year at Mulund.</p>
      <p>It is said that do not follow where the path may lead, go instead where there is no path and leave a trail. We proved it in our <b>1st project</b> under newly developed "Prasad Constructions" in 1988. In spite of all adversities, a beautiful temple of Shree Ram Siddhi Vinayak was erected 1100 feet above sea level at Kanakeshwar.</p>
      <p>We believe that Navnath Group is born for a purpose and is blessed with the power to achieve it. In 1991 we reached a landmark when <b>10th residential project</b> was completed successfully by "Prasad Constructions" coincidently at the same place – Mulund, where we had started 16 years back.</p>
      <p>We worked hard in silence and let our success to become the noise. Almost 20 years after our start of this journey, in 2006 we had completed our <b>1st commercial project</b> of Transworld Infotech Limited which is an international call center in Pimpri, Pune. The project was executed under "Mukul Constructions" and it was 3rd in a row for this newly developed firm in 2001.</p>
      <p>The whole difference between construction and creation is that a thing constructed can only be loved after it is constructed but a thing created is loved before it exists. Shrirang Niwas is our own creation that took place in 2009. It is a home of B. C. Joshi and his son who are the founder of Navnath Group. This is a place where our feet may leave but our heart will always be in. This is a place which reminds us that we will never make it our milestones if we can’t make it through our moments.</p>
      <p>If you are persistent, you will get it. If you are consistent you will keep it. The legacy of this business inspires us even after 4 decades. In 2016, we have finished another landmark project that has been executed by "Navnath Infrastructures Private Limited". This is the 1st residential project in Dapoli and the <b>20th successful project</b> in the list.</p>
